# RAGrig Skills

When asked to operate RAGrig, load and follow the appropriate skill file:

| User intent | Skill file |
|-------------|-----------|
| Set up / bootstrap | `skills/ragrig-setup.md` |
| Run an evaluation / benchmark | `skills/ragrig-evaluate.md` |
| Export / analyze results / open notebook | `skills/ragrig-analyze.md` |
| Diagnose a failure / something not working | `skills/ragrig-troubleshoot.md` |

For project architecture, API reference, and env vars: `AGENTS.md`
